"In the middle of summer, the shores of Qinghai Lake are full of golden flowers and thousands of bees, where the altitude is high, the temperature difference between day and night is large, and the air pollution is low, and the intense light gives birth to the most tenacious and generous bee colonies, creating the characteristics of Qinghai royal jelly, which is high in activity, high in protein, rich in nutritional value, low in sugar and low in fat."
