The picture shows a sea of rapeseed flowers on the shores of Qinghai Lake.
This spring, due to the need to set up road checkpoints for epidemic prevention and control, beekeepers' journey to "chase flowers for honey" was blocked, and many bees died due to missing the flowering period and lack of food, which seriously affected the income of beekeepers.
